Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with image datasets and focuses on improving the quality of Fashion MNIST, which is a computer vision task. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the impact of near-duplicate images on machine learning models and proposes a dataset with near-duplicates removed. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with improving the accuracy of machine learning models, which falls under the umbrella of AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper may involve the use of neural networks to train and test machine learning models. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper may involve the use of algorithms to identify and remove near-duplicate images from the dataset.
